  (text "NOTES:\n1. PoE injector powered via Witty Pi switched 12V rail - camera boots with Pi, sleeps with Pi\n2. No heaters installed (Sukabumi tropical climate, solar power budget constraint)\n3. Conformal coat (MG 422C silicone) on Pi, Witty Pi, Pi-EzConnect PCBs\n4. Status LEDs: Green=OK, Yellow=Working, Red=Error (all via 330R series resistors)\n5. Long press (3s) maintenance button (GPIO23) enters WiFi hotspot mode\n6. ANNKE C1200 has built-in IR LEDs - no separate IR illuminator needed\n7. Dielectric grease on all outdoor connections (cable glands, SMA, RJ45)\n8. Gore vent on compute enclosure for pressure equalization"
